        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="源码"><a href="#源码" class="headerlink" title="源码"></a><a href="https://github.com/zong4/Settle-image">源码</a></h1><h1 id="介绍"><a href="#介绍" class="headerlink" title="介绍"></a>介绍</h1><p>分别需要修改图片源路径，处理图片存放路径，文件的开头以及相关格式。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Path</span></span><br><span class="line">imagePath = <span class="string">r&quot;D:\Users\Zong\Desktop\source&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">imagePathSettled = <span class="string">r&quot;D:\Code\Blog\source\gallery\travel\Nanjing\Sceneries&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">filePath = imagePathSettled + <span class="string">&#x27;\\&#x27;</span> + <span class="string">&#x27;index.md&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">imagePathWritten = <span class="string">&quot;../gallery/travel/Nanjing/Sceneries/&quot;</span> + <span class="string">&#x27;source&#x27;</span> + <span class="string">&#x27;/&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># The string written</span></span><br><span class="line">markdownWriteString = <span class="string">&quot;---&quot;</span> + <span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span> + <span class="string">&quot;title: 风景&quot;</span> + <span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span> + <span class="string">&quot;date: 2022-06-01 20:20:08&quot;</span> + <span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span> + <span class="string">&quot;---&quot;</span> + <span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span> + <span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">markdownWriteString = markdownWriteString + <span class="string">&quot;&#123;% gallery %&#125;&quot;</span> + <span class="string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span> + <span class="string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>为了统一图片格式，均使用了默认后缀名 <strong>.jpg</strong> 。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Rename and sort</span></span><br><span class="line">index = <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> imageName <span class="keyword">in</span> os.listdir(imagePath):</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    image = cv2.imread(imagePath + <span class="string">&#x27;\\&#x27;</span> + imageName)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># All is .jpg</span></span><br><span class="line">    cv2.imwrite(imagePathSettled + <span class="string">&#x27;\\source\\&#x27;</span> + <span class="string">&#x27;&#123;&#125;.jpg&#x27;</span>.<span class="built_in">format</span>(index), image)</span><br><span class="line">    markdownWriteString = markdownWriteString + <span class="string">&quot;![](&quot;</span> + imagePathWritten + <span class="string">&#x27;&#123;&#125;.jpg&#x27;</span>.<span class="built_in">format</span>(index) + <span class="string">&quot;)&quot;</span> + <span class="string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">    index = index + <span class="number">1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="操作须知"><a href="#操作须知" class="headerlink" title="操作须知"></a>操作须知</h1><ol><li>本代码主要用于 <strong>Hexo</strong> 的 <strong>butterfly</strong> 主题下的 <strong>gallery</strong> 展示，当然其它地方亦可使用。</li><li>pip install opencv2</li><li>如果不需要创建 <strong>index.md</strong> 文件，可以将相关代码注释。</li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
